To configure this app include in your Installed app
'account'

It relies on the:
-  'django_lifecycle' package so install 'pip install django-lifecycle' and add it to the installed package as : 'django_lifecycle_checks',
- install ' pip install djangorestframework-simplejwt', add to installed apps ''


This module support:
- User creation.
- Profile management 
- 

include this varible in your `.env`
OTP_EMAIL_VERIFY_EXPIRY_TIME = your-desired-time
OTP_PASSWORD_RESET_EXPIRY_TIME = your-desired-time
FRONTEND_URL = your-frontend url